    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re not a shepherd—you’re an athlete!  Team up with a friend or ride solo and speed through dynamic, fast-paced levels, herding sheep in a futuristic medieval competition. <strong>Explode</strong>, <strong>Teleport</strong>, <strong>Warp</strong> to enhance your parkour skills and outmaneuver the flock. Compete  for the top spot on the global leaderboard—because in this world, catching sheep is the ultimate test of speed and skill!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Features:</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>COOP RACE</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You and your friends have been handpicked to compete in the prestigious Sheep Seeker World Tournament, where only the best can seek out the hidden sheep across dynamic levels.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113650/extras/62ac57b0a9ce63fe14785a73470ff43c.poster.avif?t=1754303509\" width=716 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113650/extras/62ac57b0a9ce63fe14785a73470ff43c.webm?t=1754303509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113650/extras/62ac57b0a9ce63fe14785a73470ff43c.mp4?t=1754303509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>SOLO GAMEMODE</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also play solo and compete against players from around the world!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113650/extras/e86f113e9b18887a2560db2834542820.poster.avif?t=1754303509\" width=716 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113650/extras/e86f113e9b18887a2560db2834542820.webm?t=1754303509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113650/extras/e86f113e9b18887a2560db2834542820.mp4?t=1754303509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>UNIQUE LOADOUTS</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Before each run, craft your strategy and select your unique loadout to maximize your performance.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113650/extras/5dcfbed5d93508e9ef081551594052c8.poster.avif?t=1754303509\" width=716 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113650/extras/5dcfbed5d93508e9ef081551594052c8.webm?t=1754303509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113650/extras/5dcfbed5d93508e9ef081551594052c8.mp4?t=1754303509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>A LEADERBOARD</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improve your times with smart strategies and shortcuts to race to the top of the global leaderboards. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113650/extras/1c76fccad8e960c479df3a3821323701.avif?t=1754303509\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113650/extras_big/1c76fccad8e960c479df3a3821323701.avif?t=1754303509 width=1600 height=896 /></span></p>",
